title: Texas teen charged with killing 10 in high school massacre
text:
Texas teen charged with killing 10 in high school massacre 2:25pm BST - 01:55
Multiple people were killed on Friday in a shooting at a high school in Santa Fe, Texas, a law enforcement source said, in the latest gun violence in a country still shaken by the massacre at a Florida high school in February. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
